{
  "meta": {
    "is_partial": true,
    "description": "카테고리 브레드크럼 경로 (카테고리 선택 시에만 표시, 마지막 항목에 × 삭제)"
  },
  "type": "basic",
  "name": "Div",
  "if": "{{query.category && query.category !== 'all'}}",
  "props": { "className": "flex items-center gap-1.5 text-base flex-wrap my-4 px-4 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50 rounded-lg" },
  "children": [
    {
      "comment": "전체 링크",
      "type": "basic",
      "name": "Button",
      "props": { "className": "text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-900 dark:hover:text-white" },
      "text": "$t:shop.category.all",
      "actions": [
        { "type": "click", "handler": "navigate", "params": { "path": "{{_global.shopBase}}/products", "query": {} } }
      ]
    },
    {
      "comment": "1단계 브레드크럼 (d2 이상 선택 시 - 클릭 가능)",
      "type": "basic",
      "name": "Div",
      "if": "{{!!query.d1 && !!query.d2}}",
      "props": { "className": "flex items-center gap-1" },
      "children": [
        { "type": "basic", "name": "Icon", "props": { "name": "chevron-right", "className": "w-3 h-3 text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500" } },
        {
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Button",
          "props": { "className": "text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-900 dark:hover:text-white" },
          "text": "{{(categories?.data ?? []).find(c => c.id == query.d1)?.name_localized ?? ''}}",
          "actions": [
            { "type": "click", "handler": "navigate", "params": { "path": "{{_global.shopBase}}/products", "query": { "category": "{{query.d1}}", "d1": "{{query.d1}}" } } }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "comment": "2단계 브레드크럼 (d3 이상 선택 시 - 클릭 가능)",
      "type": "basic",
      "name": "Div",
      "if": "{{!!query.d2 && !!query.d3}}",
      "props": { "className": "flex items-center gap-1" },
      "children": [
        { "type": "basic", "name": "Icon", "props": { "name": "chevron-right", "className": "w-3 h-3 text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500" } },
        {
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Button",
          "props": { "className": "text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-900 dark:hover:text-white" },
          "text": "{{((categories?.data ?? []).find(c => c.id == query.d1)?.children ?? []).find(c => c.id == query.d2)?.name_localized ?? ''}}",
          "actions": [
            { "type": "click", "handler": "navigate", "params": { "path": "{{_global.shopBase}}/products", "query": { "category": "{{query.d2}}", "d1": "{{query.d1}}", "d2": "{{query.d2}}" } } }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "comment": "3단계 브레드크럼 (4단계 선택 시 - 클릭 가능)",
      "type": "basic",
      "name": "Div",
      "if": "{{!!query.d3 && query.category != query.d3}}",
      "props": { "className": "flex items-center gap-1" },
      "children": [
        { "type": "basic", "name": "Icon", "props": { "name": "chevron-right", "className": "w-3 h-3 text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500" } },
        {
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Button",
          "props": { "className": "text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-900 dark:hover:text-white" },
          "text": "{{(((categories?.data ?? []).find(c => c.id == query.d1)?.children ?? []).find(c => c.id == query.d2)?.children ?? []).find(c => c.id == query.d3)?.name_localized ?? ''}}",
          "actions": [
            { "type": "click", "handler": "navigate", "params": { "path": "{{_global.shopBase}}/products", "query": { "category": "{{query.d3}}", "d1": "{{query.d1}}", "d2": "{{query.d2}}", "d3": "{{query.d3}}" } } }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "comment": "현재 카테고리 (마지막 항목, 굵게 + × 삭제 버튼)",
      "type": "basic",
      "name": "Div",
      "props": { "className": "flex items-center gap-1" },
      "children": [
        { "type": "basic", "name": "Icon", "props": { "name": "chevron-right", "className": "w-3 h-3 text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500" } },
        {
          "comment": "1단계 선택 (d1만, d2 없음) - 현재 카테고리명 + × 삭제",
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Div",
          "if": "{{!!query.d1 && !query.d2}}",
          "props": { "className": "flex items-center gap-1" },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Span",
              "props": { "className": "text-gray-900 dark:text-white font-semibold" },
              "text": "{{(categories?.data ?? []).find(c => c.id == query.category)?.name_localized ?? ''}}"
            },
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Button",
              "props": { "className": "ml-1 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-red-500 dark:hover:text-red-400 transition-colors" },
              "text": "×",
              "actions": [
                { "type": "click", "handler": "navigate", "params": { "path": "{{_global.shopBase}}/products", "query": {} } }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "comment": "2단계 선택 (d2 있고, d3 없음) - × 클릭 시 1단계로",
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Div",
          "if": "{{!!query.d2 && !query.d3}}",
          "props": { "className": "flex items-center gap-1" },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Span",
              "props": { "className": "text-gray-900 dark:text-white font-semibold" },
              "text": "{{((categories?.data ?? []).find(c => c.id == query.d1)?.children ?? []).find(c => c.id == query.category)?.name_localized ?? ''}}"
            },
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Button",
              "props": { "className": "ml-1 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-red-500 dark:hover:text-red-400 transition-colors" },
              "text": "×",
              "actions": [
                { "type": "click", "handler": "navigate", "params": { "path": "{{_global.shopBase}}/products", "query": { "category": "{{query.d1}}", "d1": "{{query.d1}}" } } }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "comment": "3단계 선택 (d3 있고, category == d3) - × 클릭 시 2단계로",
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Div",
          "if": "{{!!query.d3 && query.category == query.d3}}",
          "props": { "className": "flex items-center gap-1" },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Span",
              "props": { "className": "text-gray-900 dark:text-white font-semibold" },
              "text": "{{(((categories?.data ?? []).find(c => c.id == query.d1)?.children ?? []).find(c => c.id == query.d2)?.children ?? []).find(c => c.id == query.category)?.name_localized ?? ''}}"
            },
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Button",
              "props": { "className": "ml-1 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-red-500 dark:hover:text-red-400 transition-colors" },
              "text": "×",
              "actions": [
                { "type": "click", "handler": "navigate", "params": { "path": "{{_global.shopBase}}/products", "query": { "category": "{{query.d2}}", "d1": "{{query.d1}}", "d2": "{{query.d2}}" } } }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "comment": "4단계 선택 (d3 있고, category != d3) - × 클릭 시 3단계로",
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Div",
          "if": "{{!!query.d3 && query.category != query.d3}}",
          "props": { "className": "flex items-center gap-1" },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Span",
              "props": { "className": "text-gray-900 dark:text-white font-semibold" },
              "text": "{{((((categories?.data ?? []).find(c => c.id == query.d1)?.children ?? []).find(c => c.id == query.d2)?.children ?? []).find(c => c.id == query.d3)?.children ?? []).find(c => c.id == query.category)?.name_localized ?? ''}}"
            },
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Button",
              "props": { "className": "ml-1 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-red-500 dark:hover:text-red-400 transition-colors" },
              "text": "×",
              "actions": [
                { "type": "click", "handler": "navigate", "params": { "path": "{{_global.shopBase}}/products", "query": { "category": "{{query.d3}}", "d1": "{{query.d1}}", "d2": "{{query.d2}}", "d3": "{{query.d3}}" } } }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
